{"tid":1009621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有熟食檔重用蠔殼售賣　陳肇始疑講錯：全力支持環保","createTime":"2019-02-05T10:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T10:49:19.000Z","uid":35365,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82c0d5d518cf7cb1c786296a52a1bb307cfa24d7","tid":1009621,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:02:06.000Z","msg":"踏入大年初一，年宵市場的攤檔都收拾好準備回家過年。今早（5日）行政長官林鄭月娥及食物及衛生局局長陳肇始就到維園探訪清潔工，又派柑感謝他們工作辛勞。<br />\n<br />\n然而未知是否太早出動，陳肇始在回答問題時卻「答錯題」；被問到是否得悉有人重用蠔殼當生蠔賣，陳肇始卻回應「全力支持環保」，在記者再追問時才回應：「每一個攤檔都必須遵循食環署提供的指引」。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始今早與特首林鄭月娥到維園探望清潔工後見記者，途中有記者及到是否知悉有人循環再用蠔殼，以及有否收到投訴及食物中毒的個案；惟其時陳肇始疑似聽錯問題，以為是問到年宵市場的環保及清潔問題。她回應指，相信市民對如何在年宵市場源頭減廢、提高環保意識有很多的意見，食環署及環保局一直有保持密切溝通，強調兩局「全力支持環保」。又希望市民有環保意識，令年宵市場的環保情況變得更好。<br />\n<br />\n攤檔必須遵循食環署提供的指引<br />\n<br />\n其後有記者再次重覆有攤檔重用蠔殼的問題，陳肇始才恍然大悟，僅回應指，每一個攤檔都必須遵循食環署提供的指引；其後就未有回答問題離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/291777/豬年2019-有熟食檔重用蠔殼售賣-陳肇始疑講錯-全力支持環保\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F291777%2F%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B42019-%E6%9C%89%E7%86%9F%E9%A3%9F%E6%AA%94%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E8%A0%94%E6%AE%BC%E5%94%AE%E8%B3%A3-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%E7%96%91%E8%AC%9B%E9%8C%AF-%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=324b9323\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/291777/豬年2019-有熟食檔重用蠔殼售賣-陳肇始疑講錯-全力支持環保</a>"},{"pid":"f1935ca7f8e62331cfef0a3676735fe492306012","tid":1009621,"uid":35365,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"環保撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果然呢個年頭唔係弱智都做唔到官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a00cd35fa174209d89ad691560d9ca44c01aae","tid":1009621,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"搵快啲連登仔唔用dom 喺陳局長個晒到射精 咁就skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8623d6ce4441f6b0ff7b7751de850b7b6dad0b0f","tid":1009621,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"環保撚好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dd456067e4c5bc986195f403dc43077c8f00c0","tid":1009621,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18a00cd35fa174209d89ad691560d9ca44c01aae","tid":1009621,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"搵快啲連登仔唔用dom 喺陳局長個晒到射精 咁就skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a51490bc68b940fd88404f6cb14668c855bc669","tid":1009621,"uid":42268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"性病愛滋病個案增加。<br />\n<br />\n全力支持環保。"}]}